## Goal Transition Protocol

When API stabilization is complete:

1. Archive this manifest in `notes/` as `goal-history-api-stabilization.md`
2. Evaluate next goal: adapter hub, marble ecosystem, or v1.0 release
3. Reassess vision contracts — re-tier relative to the next goal
